---
import Page from '../../layouts/Page.astro'
---
<Page
  title="Pricing"
  label="Product"
  hero="Simple, honest pricing"
  sub="Free for communities. Paid for the extras. No ads ever."
  description="Krenla pricing plans — free for individuals, Pro for power users, and Community for large organizations."
>
  <div class="plan-grid">
    <div class="plan">
      <div class="plan-name">Free</div>
      <div class="plan-price">$0 <span>/ month</span></div>
      <div class="plan-desc">Everything you need to join and participate in communities.</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li>Join unlimited communities</li>
        <li>Real-time messaging</li>
        <li>Discussion threads</li>
        <li>Voice & video rooms</li>
        <li>Discovery feed</li>
        <li>Up to 3 communities you own</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="btn-plan" href="#">Get started</a>
    </div>

    <div class="plan featured">
      <div class="plan-name">Pro</div>
      <div class="plan-price">$8 <span>/ month</span></div>
      <div class="plan-desc">For people who want more out of their communities.</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li>Everything in Free</li>
        <li>Unlimited communities you own</li>
        <li>Custom profile badge</li>
        <li>Extended message history</li>
        <li>HD video in rooms</li>
        <li>Priority support</li>
        <li>Early access to new features</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="btn-plan primary" href="#">Start free trial</a>
    </div>

    <div class="plan">
      <div class="plan-name">Community</div>
      <div class="plan-price">$24 <span>/ month</span></div>
      <div class="plan-desc">For large or professional communities that need more control.</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li>Everything in Pro</li>
        <li>Advanced moderation tools</li>
        <li>Analytics dashboard</li>
        <li>Custom domain</li>
        <li>Audit logs</li>
        <li>Dedicated support contact</li>
        <li>Stage mode for 1,000+ listeners</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="btn-plan" href="#">Contact us</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">
    <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>

    <h3>Is the free plan actually free?</h3>
    <p>Yes. No credit card required, no time limit. The free plan covers everything most people need to participate fully in communities on Krenla.</p>

    <h3>Are there ads?</h3>
    <p>No. Krenla is funded by subscriptions, not advertising. We don't sell your data, and we don't run ads of any kind.</p>

    <h3>Can I cancel anytime?</h3>
    <p>Yes. Cancel from your account settings at any time. You'll keep Pro or Community features until the end of your current billing period, then revert to Free.</p>

    <h3>Do you offer discounts for nonprofits or students?</h3>
    <p>Yes — 50% off Pro and Community plans for verified nonprofits and full-time students. <a href="/company/contact">Contact us</a> with proof of eligibility.</p>

    <h3>What happens to my community if I downgrade?</h3>
    <p>Your community stays intact. If you're over the 3-community limit on Free, you'll need to transfer ownership or archive the extras before downgrading.</p>
  </div>
</Page>
